.TH VICE 1 "" "vice 9.9.9" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
vice \- test app
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vice
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fICOMMAND\fR [\fIARGS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
test app
Run \fBvice help\fR for the in-tool command summary, or \fBvice help \fI<command>\fR for per-command help.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B exit|quit
Exit the session
.TP
.B jobs
List background jobs
.TP
.B pause {id}
Pause a background job
.TP
.B resume {id}
Resume a paused job
.TP
.B cancel {id}
Cancel a background job
.TP
.B history
Show command history
.TP
.B clear
Clear the screen
.TP
.B alpha
alpha description
.TP
.B beta things {path}
beta description
.SH GLOBAL OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-chunk\-size " " \fIVALUE\fR
Byte\-stream chunk size in bytes
.TP
.BR \-\-color " " \fIVALUE\fR
Force or suppress color output (auto|always|never)
.TP
.BR \-\-depth " " \fIVALUE\fR
Maximum recursion depth
.TP
.B \-\-dry\-run
Show what would happen without making changes
.TP
.BR \-\-encoding " " \fIVALUE\fR
Text encoding (utf8|ascii)
.TP
.BR \-\-format " " \fIVALUE\fR
Output or content format (text|hex|json|...)
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help
.TP
.BR \-\-limit " " \fIVALUE\fR
Maximum results to return
.TP
.BR \-\-locale " " \fIVALUE\fR
BCP\-47 locale tag for output formatting (e.g. en\-US, de\-DE)
.TP
.BR \-\-metadata " " \fIVALUE\fR
Per\-call metadata as JSON
.TP
.B \-\-no\-color
Disable ANSI color output
.TP
.B \-\-no\-pager
Disable PAGER wrapping for long output
.TP
.B \-\-no\-status
Disable status spinner
.TP
.B \-\-non\-interactive
Refuse to prompt; fail fast on missing input
.TP
.BR \-\-offset " " \fIVALUE\fR
Skip this many results
.TP
.BR \-\-page " " \fIVALUE\fR
1\-based page number (alternative to offset)
.TP
.B \-\-quiet
Suppress non\-error output
.TP
.BR \-\-timeout " " \fIVALUE\fR
Maximum I/O wait time in milliseconds
.TP
.B \-\-verbose
Verbose output
.TP
.B \-\-version
Show version
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 1
Generic runtime error.
.TP
.B 2
Usage error (unknown command, bad argument).
.TP
.B 130
Interrupted by SIGINT (Ctrl+C).
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B VICE_LOG_LEVEL
Logger threshold (trace|debug|info|warn|error).
.TP
.B NO_COLOR, FORCE_COLOR, CLICOLOR_FORCE
Standard color-control env vars.
.TP
.B XDG_CONFIG_HOME, XDG_DATA_HOME, XDG_CACHE_HOME, XDG_STATE_HOME
Standard XDG directories. Each can be overridden per-app via VICE_CONFIG_HOME et al.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR vice (1)

